main_body:
Spain is hereby authorized to grand aid totalling Ptas 51 384 300 000 to the Spanish coal industry with effect from 1 January 1988 for the 1988 calendar year.
The total amount shall be made up of the following aids:
1. an amount not exceeding Ptas 49 029 300 000 in aid to cover operating losses;
2. an amount not exceeding Ptas 1 400 million in aid for the sale of deliveries of coal and coke to the Community iron and steel industry;
3. an amount not exceeding Ptas 605 million in investment aid;
4. an amount not exceeding Ptas 350 million in aid to promote innovation.
